boot:
    `debug 2`
    `image 1` ; System
    Please select an option.
    `drawoff`
    `setdi 0`
    `setda callMenu`
    `setdt 8 43 6f 6e 74 61 63 74 73` ; Contacts
    `setdi 1`
    `setda soundtest`
    `setdt 5 4d 75 73 69 63` ; Music
    `setdi 2`
    `setda info`
    `setdt 8 53 65 74 74 69 6e 67 73` ; Settings
    `setdi 3`
    `setda exit`
    `setdt 8 53 68 75 74 64 6f 77 6e` ; Shutdown
    `jsr menu`

menu: ; standard menu routine
    `setdi 0`
    `drawon`
    `wait`
    `drawoff`
    `pdtr $eax`
    `reset`
    `jump $eax`

callMenu:
    `reset`
    `setdi 0`
    `setdt 6 E5 FF B1 E1 C6 AE`
    `setda flagsDemo`
    `setdi 1`
    `setdt 5 C6 CE D5 71 EA`
    `setda dialtone`
    `setdi 2`
    `setdt 5 F0 FF BD 40 A8`
    `setda dialtone`
    `setdi 3`
    `setdt 4 42 61 63 6b` ; Back
    `setda boot`
    Who to call?
    `jsr menu`

flagsDemo:
    `chkflag $ah CALLED`
    `jumpne $rax 012500000000 garbage`
    `image 0` ; missingno (on purpose)
    Hello! This is M. Are you calling about-`newline`
    Wait. Who are you? How did you get this number?`newline`
    ...Don't call again. *click*
    `playsfx 0` ; click sound
    `wait`
    `setflag CALLED 1`
    `image 1` ; System
    `reset`
    `jump callMenu`

garbage:
    (The number just hung up immediately...)
    `wait`
    `jump callMenu`

info:
    `reset`
    Which option to use?
    `setdi 0`
    `setda filltests`
    `setdt 4 49 6e 66 6f` ; Info
    `setdi 1`
    `setda enableDebug`
    `setdt 9 44 65 62 75 67 4d 6f 64 65` ; DebugMode
    `chkflag $ch DEBUG_MODE`
    `jumpeq $rcx 1000000000000 debugEnabled`
    `setdi 2`
    `setdt 4 42 61 63 6b` ; Back
    `setda boot`
    `jsr menu`

filltests:
    Device Info:`newline`
        Firmware Version: `varfill 1 10`ÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿ
    `wait`
    `reset`
    `jump info`

debug:
    `reset`
    TODO
    `wait`
    `jump info`

debugEnabled:
    `setdi 2`
    `setda boot`
    `setdt 6 52 65 62 6f 6f 74` ; Reboot
    `setdi 3`
    `setda debug`
    `setdt A 41 64 76 4f 70 74 69 6f 6e 73` ; AdvOptions
    `setdi 4`
    `setdt 4 42 61 63 6b` ; Back
    `setda boot`
    `jsr menu`

enableDebug:
    `chkflag $bh DEBUG_MODE`
    `jumpeq $rbx 1000000000000 disableDebug`
    Debug Mode enabled.
    `setflag DEBUG_MODE 1`
    `wait`
    `jump info`

disableDebug:
    Debug Mode disabled.
    `setflag DEBUG_MODE 0`
    `wait`
    `jump info`

exit:
    `halt`
    `jump 0`

soundtest:
    `reset`
    What track to play?
    `wait`
    `jump boot`

dialtone:
    (No response. Just a dialtone...)
    `wait`
    `jump callMenu`